title: 10 GB of high entropy random data
description:
This torrent contains 10 GB of high entropy random data, created using hardware, rather than software. Use it for whatever reason you want.

Since it is random, it will not compress at all.

The files are splitted into 10 MB parts, so you can selectively download parts.

Usages:

- To generate encryption keys
- Testing Speed of disk drives
- Testing speed of network
- Testing efficiency of compression algorithms
- Filling someones (or your own) harddrive, either for fun or to erase empty space
